ActCanadian Air Transport Security Authority Act
PrecisAppointment of MARGARET PURDY of Vancouver, British Columbia, to be Chairperson of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority, on an interim basis, to hold office during pleasure until such time as a new Chairperson is appointed, effective January 27, 2007.
